<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema612_07_IH_0005</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_07.css" />
    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema612_07_ih_0005.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_07_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="5" class="is_star" lang="y">두 입체도형의 공통점과 차이점을 각각 써 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_07_IH/0005_01.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="input_area mt_20">
            <span class="label_gray" lang="y">공통점</span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">두 입체도형은 밑면의 모양이 모두 삼각형입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="input_area mt_20">
            <span class="label_gray" lang="y">차이점</span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">각기둥은 밑면이 2개, 각뿔은 밑면이 1개입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">두 입체도형은 밑면의 모양이 모두 삼각형이지만 각기둥은 밑면이 2개, 각뿔은 밑면이 1개입니다. 각기둥의 옆면은 모두 직사각형이고, 각뿔의 옆 면은 모두 삼각형입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit chk">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
